# Commit and PR conventions

- **Commits:** follow [`CONVENTION.md`](../../CONVENTION.md) — types, scope, body, examples.
- **Commit plans:** [`.lsi/workflows/commits-logical-order.md`](../../.lsi/workflows/commits-logical-order.md) — plan first; **commit only when the user explicitly asks**.
- **PRs:** [`.lsi/workflows/pull-requests.md`](../../.lsi/workflows/pull-requests.md) — title and body sections.
- **Examples:** `.lsi/workflows/examples/`

Do not amend, squash, or use `--no-verify` unless the user explicitly requests.
